final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.

Then, move RIGHT to reach the KeyDoor (x=18) and open it. Finally, move UP to reach the goal (x=19, y=9). Because the agent is at x=18 and y=8, it must move RIGHT 1 time and then move UP 1 time.
